title: Firefox 119 - Privacy Updates, Decades Old Bugfix, and More
description:
In this video I discuss the latest Firefox browsers update 119, which brings improvements to Firefox view, better privacy features including Encrypted Client Hello, and a Fix for a 22 year old bug by a 23 year old electrical engineering student named Yifan Zhu.

https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/119.0/releasenotes/
